Jalani saja
Just live your life

187
00:12:46,913 --> 00:12:48,513
Ma-i-ka!
Whatever!

188
00:13:08,213 --> 00:13:10,913
Comic Frontier! こんばんは！
Comic Frontier! Good evening!

189
00:13:11,213 --> 00:13:14,213
こんばんは！ こんばんは！
Good evening! Good evening!

190
00:13:15,213 --> 00:13:17,213
ようこそ...
Welcome to...

191
00:13:17,213 --> 00:13:26,713
『hololive Indonesia 5th Anniversary
LIVE Chromatic Future』へ！
hololive Indonesia 5th Anniversary
LIVE Chromatic Future!

192
00:13:27,213 --> 00:13:30,713
イェーイ！
Yay!

193
00:13:30,913 --> 00:13:33,213
ワギヤワギヤワギヤ！
Wow wow wow!

194
00:13:33,713 --> 00:13:38,513
5周年のライブに来てくれてありがとう！
Thank you for coming to our 5th anniversary live!

195
00:13:38,713 --> 00:13:42,213
まさかもう5周年とはね！
I can't believe it's already been 5 years!

196
00:13:42,713 --> 00:13:46,713
じゃあ自己紹介から始めましょうか？
まずはゼータから！
Shall we start with self-introductions?
Starting with Zeta!

197
00:13:47,213 --> 00:13:49,213
はいはいはい！
Yes, yes, yes!

198
00:13:49,713 --> 00:13:51,213
よし... あ、後ろか
Alright... oh, behind me

199
00:13:52,713 --> 00:13:56,213
アアア！ ミッションスタート！
スケート！ スケート！ スケート！
Ahhh! Mission start!
Skat! Skat! Skat!

200
00:13:56,713 --> 00:14:04,713
ホロライブインドネシア3期生の
ベスティア・ゼータです！ よろしくお願いします！
I'm Vestia Zeta from Hololive Indonesia Gen 3!
Nice to meet you!

201
00:14:05,713 --> 00:14:07,713
よろしくゼータ！ よし次はカエラ！
Nice to meet you Zeta! Alright, next is Kaela!

202
00:14:08,213 --> 00:14:16,213
はいはい！ カエロ！ 毎日鍛冶をやってる
ホロライブインドネシア3期生の鍛冶屋！
Yes! Kaelo! Grinding every day,
the blacksmith from Hololive Indonesia Gen 3!

203
00:14:16,713 --> 00:14:19,513
カエラ・コヴァルスキアです！
よろしくお願いします！
I'm Kaela Kovalskia!
Nice to meet you all!

204
00:14:19,713 --> 00:14:22,213
よろしくカエラ！ 次はこぼだ！ こぼ！
Nice to meet you Kaela! Next is Kobo! Kobo!

205
00:14:22,713 --> 00:14:26,713
やっほー！ ぼこぼこぼ～こぼ・かなえる、
アットユアサービス！
Hi! Bokobokobo~ Kobo Kanaeru,
at your service!

206
00:14:26,913 --> 00:14:30,213
君の日々を照らす太陽になりましょう！
えへっ！
Let me be the sun to shine your days!
Ehe!

207
00:14:30,713 --> 00:14:33,213
Kobokers、声を上げて！
Kobokers, let me hear your voices!

208
00:14:33,513 --> 00:14:38,213
ウォー！！
Whoaaa!!

209
00:14:38,713 --> 00:14:41,213
3人で...
The three of us...

210
00:14:41,713 --> 00:14:48,713
ホロライブインドネシア3期生、
holoh3roでーす！
Hololive Indonesia Gen 3,
we are holoh3ro!

211
00:14:52,713 --> 00:14:59,213
やあ、ついにホロライブID 5周年ライブが
できるとはね。ついにあったんだ！
Wow, finally a Hololive ID 5th anniversary live.
It's finally happening!

212
00:14:59,713 --> 00:15:03,713
1曲目からもうめっちゃカッコいいよね！
その熱き、感じてるわ！
The first song was already so cool!
I'm really feeling the heat!

213
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:05,472
Ya ampun, asik banget ya, iya nggak sih? Iya nggak sih?
Oh my god, it's so fun, right? Don't you think?

214
00:15:05,472 --> 00:15:05,972
Parah sih!
It's crazy!

215
00:15:05,972 --> 00:15:09,472
Adrenalinnya berasa kan ya? Pengen lari aku rasanya nih!
You can feel the adrenaline, right? I feel like running!

216
00:15:09,472 --> 00:15:12,672
Woi woi woi woi woi! Mau ke mana?
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey! Where are you going?

217
00:15:12,672 --> 00:15:17,772
Iya iya iya stop stop stop stop stop stop stop!
Okay, okay, okay, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop!

218
00:15:17,772 --> 00:15:20,672
Nanti keringetan lho! Nanti keringetan!
You'll get all sweaty! You'll get sweaty!

219
00:15:21,472 --> 00:15:22,672
Ah, kalau Kaela gimana?
Ah, what about you, Kaela?

220
00:15:22,672 --> 00:15:27,372
Aduh, seru banget. Aku nggak nyangka sih, sampai aku bisa ada di sini ya.
Wow, it's so much fun. I never expected that I could be standing here.

221
00:15:27,672 --> 00:15:32,372
Tapi ini ngomong-ngomong, konsernya masih panjang banget, jadi kalian tetep semangat ya sampai akhir!
But by the way, the concert is still very long, so keep your spirit up until the end!

222
00:15:33,172 --> 00:15:37,172
Semangat semangat semangat semangat semangat!
Let's go, let's go, let's go, let's go, let's go!

223
00:15:38,172 --> 00:15:42,372
Eh tapi ngomongin konser dari tadi, emang pada tahu judul konsernya apa?
But speaking of the concert, do you guys know what the title is?

224
00:15:43,172 --> 00:15:47,472
Judul konser kita kali ini adalah 'Chromatic Future'!
The title of our concert this time is 'Chromatic Future'!

225
00:15:47,472 --> 00:15:49,672
Ada yang tahu nggak artinya apa? Ayo absen!
Does anyone know what it means? Let's check!

226
00:15:50,172 --> 00:15:53,172
Nah, ini, Kobo paling tahu.
Now, this, Kobo knows best.

227
00:15:54,172 --> 00:15:56,172
Heh? Ah...
Huh? Ah...

228
00:15:56,372 --> 00:15:59,972
Yang jelasin yang paling tinggi, yuk let's go!
The tallest one should explain, let's go!

229
00:16:00,672 --> 00:16:02,672
Segitu ya... ya sudahlah... ya sudahlah...
Is that how it is? Well, fine... fine...

230
00:16:03,172 --> 00:16:08,372
Nih ya guys ya buat kalian yang belum tahu, 'Chromatic Future' itu artinya tuh masa depan yang berwarna-warni.
So guys, for those who don't know, 'Chromatic Future' means a colorful future.

231
00:16:09,172 --> 00:16:11,672
Jadi karena Hololive Indonesia kan udah 5 tahun nih...
Since Hololive Indonesia has been around for 5 years now...

232
00:16:12,172 --> 00:16:15,372
Kita sama-sama dari hari satu sampai sekarang...
We've been walking together from day one until now...

233
00:16:16,172 --> 00:16:18,472
Nah jadi itu untuk ke depannya kita tuh juga harapannya tuh kita bisa nyiptain waktu...
So for the future, our hope is that we can create time...

234
00:16:18,472 --> 00:16:23,672
...dan memori yang berwarna-warni...
...and colorful memories...

235
00:16:23,672 --> 00:16:26,672
...sama seluruh fans dari Hololive Indonesia!
...together with all the fans of Hololive Indonesia!

236
00:16:27,172 --> 00:16:31,372
Ya gitu, betul Kaela Kovalskia! Catat, catat!
That's right, Kaela Kovalskia is correct! Take notes!

237
00:16:31,372 --> 00:16:33,172
Iya iya iya...
Yes, yes, yes...

238
00:16:34,372 --> 00:16:38,672
Nah, kalian sekarang udah pada tahu kan karena tadi udah dijelasin sama Kaela.
Now you all know, since Kaela just explained it.

239
00:16:39,172 --> 00:16:41,472
Kalau gitu, konsernya kan udah mulai nih...
Since the concert has already started...

240
00:16:41,472 --> 00:16:45,172
Kalian mau nge-post soal konser ini di medsos...
...when you post about this concert on social media...

241
00:16:45,172 --> 00:16:50,172
...jangan lupa hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture ya!
...don't forget the hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture!

242
00:16:51,172 --> 00:16:55,672
Karena kita pengen banget lihat kalian tuh... apa sih...
Because we really want to see your... what is it...

243
00:16:55,672 --> 00:16:58,972
...pengen lihat semangat kalian!
...we want to see your passion!

244
00:17:00,172 --> 00:17:02,372
Ya itu betul banget, iya nggak?
Yeah, that's absolutely right!

245
00:17:03,172 --> 00:17:04,672
Jangan typo, jangan typo!
No typos, no typos!

246
00:17:05,172 --> 00:17:08,372
Asik, share ke semua, oke?
Nice, share it with everyone, okay?

247
00:17:09,472 --> 00:17:15,672
Jadi tapi jujur deh, kalian tuh pas dibilang kita bakal konser lho di Indonesia, kalian pada kaget nggak sih?
But honestly, when you were told we'd have a concert in Indonesia, were you guys surprised?

248
00:17:15,672 --> 00:17:17,672
Halo, ada yang dengerin?
Hello, is anyone listening?

249
00:17:19,172 --> 00:17:21,472
Ayo ayo...
Come on, come on...

250
00:17:22,172 --> 00:17:24,372
Betul, aku setuju juga.
That's right, I agree too.

251
00:17:25,172 --> 00:17:28,472
Aku merasakan empati terhadap ini adik saya Zeta.
I feel empathy for my little sister Zeta here.

252
00:17:29,172 --> 00:17:30,472
Empati iya iya...
Empathy, yes, yes...

253
00:17:30,472 --> 00:17:31,672
Kalau Kaela gimana, Kaela Kovalskia?
What about you, Kaela Kovalskia?

254
00:17:31,672 --> 00:17:35,672
Aku juga waktu itu nggak nyangka banget kayak 'hah, beneran nih? Real nih?' gitu kan.
I also didn't expect it at all, like 'huh, for real? Is this real?'

255
00:17:36,172 --> 00:17:42,372
Kayak 'lho, bisa gitu? Akhirnya... mana udah bersembilan di Indonesia pula ya kan?'
Like 'wow, it's finally happening... and all nine of us in Indonesia too, right?'

256
00:17:43,172 --> 00:17:46,372
Keren banget! Keren banget!
It's so cool! It's so cool!

257
00:17:47,172 --> 00:17:50,672
Ini kan konser pertama Hololive Indonesia yang bersembilan.
This is the first Hololive Indonesia concert with all nine members.

258
00:17:51,172 --> 00:17:55,672
Sebenarnya tuh nggak hanya ini tuh momen terbesar dan terpenting juga untuk fans Hololive Indonesia...
Actually, it's not just the biggest and most important moment for Hololive Indonesia fans...

259
00:17:55,672 --> 00:18:00,172
...tapi seluruh dunia juga pasti bakal nonton nggak sih?
...but everyone around the world must be watching, right?

260
00:18:03,172 --> 00:18:04,372
Iya nggak?
Right?

261
00:18:05,172 --> 00:18:07,372
Iya, jawab!
Yes, answer me!

262
00:18:08,172 --> 00:18:10,472
Iya iya makasih, makasih semuanya...
Yes, yes, thank you, thank you everyone...

263
00:18:10,672 --> 00:18:15,372
...tapi tentu saja ini pencapaiannya nggak bakal cuma sampai di sini aja kan?
...but of course, this achievement won't just stop here, right?

264
00:18:16,172 --> 00:18:19,672
Jadi next-nya mungkin kita bisa apa ya... dominating the world gitu.
So next, maybe we can... like, dominate the world.

265
00:18:20,172 --> 00:18:21,472
We are ready, we ready ready!
We are ready, we're ready, ready!

266
00:18:21,672 --> 00:18:26,672
Ready ready ready! Betul banget Kaela, Zeta!
Ready, ready, ready! You're absolutely right, Kaela and Zeta!

267
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:31,472
Selain dari dukungan fans in this opportunity, kita juga mau mengucapkan terima kasih...
In addition to the fans' support on this opportunity, we also want to say thank you...

268
00:18:31,472 --> 00:18:36,372
...untuk semua sponsor yang mendukung terjadinya konser ini. Terima kasih!
...to all the sponsors who supported the realization of this concert. Thank you!

269
00:18:36,372 --> 00:18:43,672
Terima kasih! Makasih makasih makasih semuanya! Thank you thank you thank you!
Thank you! Thank you, thank you, thank you everyone! Thank you, thank you, thank you!

270
00:18:44,172 --> 00:18:48,372
Eh tapi ngomong-ngomong di konser ini kayaknya ada yang beda nggak sih?
By the way, doesn't something feel different about this concert?

271
00:18:48,372 --> 00:18:52,472
Ela, kamu nyadar nggak? Soalnya kamu paling peka nggak sih?
Ela, did you notice? You're the most observant one, right?

272
00:18:53,172 --> 00:18:57,472
Wits... ya sadarlah, kalau Kobo mah nggak bakal sadar.
Wits... of course I did. Kobo wouldn't even notice.

273
00:18:58,172 --> 00:19:00,672
Nih nih nih nih yang beda tuh kali ini tuh model kita...
Look, look, look, look. What's different this time is our models...

274
00:19:00,672 --> 00:19:04,172
Ini model baru nih!
These are new models!

275
00:19:05,172 --> 00:19:07,372
Gemes banget! Lucu lucu!
So adorable! So cute!

276
00:19:07,672 --> 00:19:12,672
Wiii! Lucu lucu lucu lucu lucu!
Wheee! So cute, cute, cute, cute, cute!

277
00:19:13,172 --> 00:19:17,372
Kameranya dekatin ke aku! Kameranya dekatin ke aku!
Bring the camera closer to me! Bring the camera closer to me!

278
00:19:17,672 --> 00:19:21,472
Nih nih nih nih kalian mau lihat keimutan Kobo nih nih...
Look, look, look, look! You guys want to see Kobo's cuteness? Here, here...

279
00:19:22,172 --> 00:19:23,372
Oshiri!
Butt!

280
00:19:23,372 --> 00:19:25,172
Eh eh eh eh...
Hey, hey, hey, hey...

281
00:19:26,172 --> 00:19:30,672
Wait wait wait wait, ini kamera diambil Kobo semua nggak sih? Ini ke aku aku juga aku juga!
Wait, wait, wait, wait, Kobo is hogging all the cameras, right? Here, to me too, me too!

282
00:19:30,672 --> 00:19:34,372
Jangan Kobo doang!
Not just Kobo!

283
00:19:35,172 --> 00:19:38,372
Sini sini sini sini kamera kamera kamera Kobo lagi!
Here, here, here, here, camera, camera, camera! Kobo's turn again!

284
00:19:39,172 --> 00:19:45,372
Stop stop stop stop stop stop stop stop stop! Mulai mulai mulai semua kamera diambil!
Stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop! She's starting again, taking all the cameras!

285
00:19:45,372 --> 00:19:47,172
Semua kamera diambil!
She's hogging all the cameras!

286
00:19:47,172 --> 00:19:48,372
Oke oke oke...
Okay, okay, okay...

287
00:19:49,172 --> 00:19:53,672
Kalau gitu... aduh aduh aduh sampai kehabisan napas... Jangan rebutan di depan konser!
Alright then... wow, I'm out of breath... Don't fight in front of the concert!

288
00:19:58,172 --> 00:19:59,372
Iya...
Okay...

289
00:20:00,172 --> 00:20:01,372
Iya iya iya...
Yes, yes, yes...

290
00:20:02,172 --> 00:20:04,172
Zeta kalau marah serem lho.
Zeta is scary when she's angry.

291
00:20:03,816 --> 00:20:05,916
はいよ ゼータが怒ると怖いからね
Okay, because Zeta's scary when she's angry.

292
00:20:05,916 --> 00:20:07,116
こわいよー
Scary!

293
00:20:07,116 --> 00:20:12,916
もういいや ゼータがカメラも独り占めしちゃダメっていうのは… うーん、しょうがない
Fine, if we can't hog the camera from Zeta... Hmm, I guess it can't be helped.

294
00:20:12,916 --> 00:20:15,616
ファンのみんなと遊ぼう！
Let's play with the fans!

295
00:20:15,616 --> 00:20:19,916
さっきみんなからも大きな声もらったわけだし 今度はこっちがみんなに大きな声を出したいっす！
Everyone gave us their loud voices earlier, so now it's our turn to give a loud voice to everyone!

296
00:20:19,916 --> 00:20:21,116
はいはいはい
Yes yes yes.

297
00:20:21,116 --> 00:20:25,816
そうっすよ、カエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's right, it won't be as long as Kaela's stream time so don't worry.

298
00:20:25,816 --> 00:20:28,816
そう！ みんなにじゃなく、みんなとね
Right! Not *at* everyone, but *with* everyone.

299
00:20:28,816 --> 00:20:30,916
そうそう！ そういうことっす！
Yeah! That's what I mean!

300
00:20:30,916 --> 00:20:35,716
だってこれから歌わなきゃいけないから まず声を温存しなきゃでしょ？
Because we have to sing after this, we need to save our voices first, right?

301
00:20:35,916 --> 00:20:42,716
そうっすよ、そんなにカエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's right, it won't be as long as Kaela's stream time so don't worry.

302
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:46,916
まあいい 大声出していいから好きにして
Well fine, you can shout as much as you want.

303
00:20:46,916 --> 00:20:49,916
みんな準備はいいかな？
Everyone, are you ready?

304
00:20:50,116 --> 00:20:52,616
準備出来てる？
Are you ready?

305
00:20:52,616 --> 00:20:57,716
もう出来てるみたいっすね！ じゃあここから！
Seems like you're already ready! Then from here!

306
00:20:57,716 --> 00:21:04,616
一緒に「BOKOBOKOBO！」って叫ぼう！ よろしくいくよ！
Let's shout "BOKOBOKOBO" together! Here we go!

307
00:21:05,616 --> 00:21:08,716
いち、に、さん！
One, two, three!

308
00:21:08,716 --> 00:21:13,716
BOKOBOKOBO！
BOKOBOKOBO!

309
00:21:14,716 --> 00:21:16,916
いいわねいいわね！次はゼータ！
Good, good! Next is Zeta!

310
00:21:16,916 --> 00:21:18,716
はいはいはいはい！
Yes yes yes yes!

311
00:21:18,716 --> 00:21:24,816
「ミッションスタート」って言ったら一緒に「スタート」って言ってわね！
When I say "Mission Start", say "Start" together!

312
00:21:24,816 --> 00:21:27,816
いいかな？ アアア！ ミッション…
Ready? Ahhh! Mission...

313
00:21:27,816 --> 00:21:31,816
スタート！
Start!

314
00:21:34,816 --> 00:21:36,316
次はカエラ！
Next is Kaela!

315
00:21:36,316 --> 00:21:40,716
よしよしよしよし！ きてみんもそしてholoh3roも
Good good good good! To the audience and holoh3ro too.

316
00:21:40,716 --> 00:21:46,316
「holoh3ro！」って言ったら「HU-HA！」で返してね！ 簡単でしょ？
When I say "holoh3ro!", respond with "HU-HA!"! Easy, right?

317
00:21:46,316 --> 00:21:48,716
さあさあさあ！
Come on, come on, come on!

318
00:21:48,716 --> 00:21:51,816
準備はいい？ holoh3ro！
Are you ready? holoh3ro!

319
00:21:51,816 --> 00:21:53,816
HU-HA！
HU-HA!

320
00:21:53,816 --> 00:21:58,716
いいわねいいわね！
Good, good!

321
00:21:58,716 --> 00:22:03,716
いいわね ついに３期生は息ぴったり
Nice, finally Gen 3 is in perfect sync.

322
00:22:03,716 --> 00:22:07,816
そうね まだまだ元気が有り余りそうね
Yeah, looks like there's still plenty of energy left.

323
00:22:07,816 --> 00:22:11,816
だって、今日の一曲目だもん でももうすごく伝わってくるんだもん
After all, it's the first song of the day. But it's already coming through so much.

324
00:22:11,816 --> 00:22:16,916
みんな、まさか私達の一曲目が「100%」だなんて思ってた？
Everyone, did you ever think our first song would be "100%"?

325
00:22:16,916 --> 00:22:20,816
思うわけないよな 私もびっくりした
No way we'd think that. I was surprised too.

326
00:22:20,816 --> 00:22:24,816
ホシノヴァ気分でライブ開始だなんて！ すごいよね？
Starting the live in Hoshinova mood! Amazing, isn't it?

327
00:22:24,816 --> 00:22:25,816
やばい！
Crazy!

328
00:22:25,816 --> 00:22:30,816
かっこいいっすね、しかもさっきゼータと歌った… いや違う
It's cool, and singing with Zeta earlier... No wait.

329
00:22:30,816 --> 00:22:31,816
ゼータとか？
Zeta or something?

330
00:22:31,816 --> 00:22:35,816
ゼータとカエラが歌った時はもう本家の「100%」みたいっす
When Zeta and Kaela sang, it was just like the original "100%".

331
00:22:35,816 --> 00:22:41,816
マジかっこよすぎなんだけど なんか、うーうー！ってなってきて！
It was seriously too cool, I was like "Ugh! Ugh!".

332
00:22:41,816 --> 00:22:44,716
あんなにかっこいい歌を歌ったことあるのかな？
I wonder if I've ever sung such a cool song before?

333
00:22:44,716 --> 00:22:45,916
かっこつけてんの？
Are you trying to look cool?

334
00:22:45,916 --> 00:22:46,916
そう、かっこつけてる
Yeah, acting cool.

335
00:22:46,916 --> 00:22:51,716
